ader world’s most admired companies fortune winner most valuable military employer civilianjobscom best companies for leadership chief executiveth consecutive year dow jones sustainability indices dow jones cdp a list climate cdpour legacyin  frederick stanley started a small shop in new britain connecticut to manufacture bolts hinges and other hardware of high quality from wrought iron in  duncan black and alonzo decker started their shop in baltimore maryland and six years later obtained the world’s first patent for a portable power tool over the years the two companies amassed an unparalleled family of iconic brands and trusted products in  they came together as stanley black  decker a leading global diversified industrial known for superior quality continual innovation and rigorous operational discipline we remain driven by a passion for excellence and a commitment to serve the builders makers and protectors of the world httpwwwstanleyblackanddeckercomsitesdefaultfilesfactoidmetallinesjpg a leading global diversified industrialbased on revenuehttpwwwstanleyblackanddeckercomsitesdefaultfilesfactoidmetallinesjpgin tools and storagein security servicesgloballeaderin engineered fastening•••share facebook twitter linkedin emailhttpwwwstanleyblackanddeckercomsitesdefaultfilesstylesmorefromuspublicaboutusmorejpgitokqlrovsxy culturebold and agile yet thoughtful and determined leadershiptenured talented dedicated  social responsibilityour impact in the world move to top stocks index  markets index bulletin investor alert new york markets close in market snapshot winners and losers stocks rates funds bonds benchmarks real estate investment trusts futures american depository receipt stocks exchange traded notes warrants indexes exchange traded funds currencies crypto currencies browse stocks stocks az abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzother browse by location argentina australia austria bahamas bahrain belgium bermuda botswana brazil british virgin islands canada cayman islands ch