onvergent security solutions css  mechanical access solutions mas  divested businesses  hardware and home improvement hhi  air compressors and pressure washers  tools  notes  further reading  external links historyedit the company came to existence as a direct result of the  merger of stanleys bolt manufactory founded by frederick trent stanley in  and the stanley rule and level company founded by fredericks cousin henry stanley in  during world war ii stanley works received the armynavy e award for excellence in war production wwii armynavy production award to stanley works presentation program january   in may  the company considered moving its corporate headquarters to bermuda but public and governmental outcry forced management to reconsider the move by august  the company had decided to maintain its incorporation in the united states john f lundgren was elected as chairman and chief executive officer in  replacing john trani a former protégé of jack welch at general electric the hardware  home improvement group including the kwikset weiser baldwin national hardware stanley fanal pfister and ezset brands was acquired by spectrum brands holdings inc on december   acquisitionsedit  stanley works entered the uk market with the acquisition of ja chapman of sheffield england  stanley works acquired north brothers manufacturing company  stanley started operations in australia as stanleytitan when it bought a  share of titan a subsidiary of bhp  stanley works acquired vidmar cabinets  stanleytitan acquired turner tools based in melbourne australia  stanley works acquired mac tools  stanley works purchased proto from ingersoll rand and it becomes stanley proto  stanley works acquired bostitch from textron  stanley works acquired goldblatt and zag industries  acquired sidchrome tool co headquartered in melbourne australia closed plant in  and started to move all tool manufacturing to taiwan whilist sourcing various items from proto in the usa marked as proto on items due to short supply of left over australian made tools being sold out until all manufacturing was up to speed in taiwan  stanley works purchased the chatsworth californiabased monarch mirror door co inc an american manufacturer of sliding and folding mirrordoors  stanley works acquired blick of swindon england a uk integrator of security solutions communication and timemanagement solutions and cst berger  in october stanley works acquired best access systems of indianapolis indiana for  million the acquisition also prompted the creation of a new access controls group for stanley further additions to this new working group included blick  in january stanley announced plans to acquire frisco bay industries ltd a canadian provider of security integration services for  million in december the acquisition of isr solutions inc headquartered in washington dc was announced isr solutions provides the us federal government and commercial customers with access security system services  in january the acquisition of security group inc was announced security group was composed of two primary operating companies sargent  greenleaf inc a manufacturer of locks and safemasters a north american provider of security installation maintenance and repair services an additional acquisition of precision hardware was made in   stanley furthered its corporate assets in the security market by acquiring hsm electronic protection systems after it had been spun off from honeywell in compliance with preemptive securities and exchange commission antitrust rulings in the meantime the company obtained security contracts as the primary contractor to secure three nasa spaceflight centers stanley works also acquired facom  late in the year stanley acquired osi security of chula vista california a provider of batteryoperated wireless lock technology and supplies to government education and healthcare industries  stanley acquired beach toolbox industries headquartered in smith falls ontario canada then closed the plant  in june stanley announced the acquisition of sonitrol which provides security systems that use audio listening devices as the primary means of intrusion detection stanley also acquired xmark corporation which provides radio frequency identification rfid solutions in healthcare environments as of  many of the stanley security services divisions were being integrated under the hsm brand  on november  stanley announced a merger with black  decker the merger was completed on march    in july the company announced the acquisition of crcevans pipeline international crcevans provides total project support for pipeline construction contractors with automatic welding and other pipeline construction specific equipment and personnel  on september  the acquisition of niscayah was complete  on january  the acquisition of lista north america headquartered in holliston massachusetts was completed  on june  the acquisition of powers fasteners headquartered in brewster new york was completed  on june  the acquisition of aeroscout inc headquartered in redwood city california was completed  stanley black  decker announced in october that it acquired the irwin lenox and hilmor tool brands for  billion from newell brands  on january  news reports indicated that it would acquire the craftsman brand from kcd llc a sears holdings subsidiary subsequent reports by bloomberg indicated that the company would pay  million initially an additional  million after three years as well as annual payments on new craftsman sales for  years business segments and brandsedit sources construction and doityourself cdiyedit power toolsedit dewalt – power tools b  d acquired in  guoqiang gq tools china – power tools portercable – power tools b  d acquired in  oldham saw company – circular saw blade and wood router bit products b  d acquired in  black  decker – acquired via merger in  stanley hand tools craftsman hand tools and storageedit pastorino – carpentry and construction hand tools stanley hand tools – carpentry and construction hand tools fastening and accessoriesedit bostitch – fastening tools acquired in  powers fasteners – adhesive and mechanical anchors industrialedit industrial and automotive repair iaredit cribmaster – tool inventory storage tracking and usagevending management expert – industrial and automotive tools facom france – professional tools acquired in  includes britool lista north america – industrial storage acquired in  mac tools – professional tools acquired in  proto – industrial hand tools acquired in  blackhawk – mechanics tools acquired in  sidchrome australianew zealand – mechanics tools acquired in  stanley supply  services – mro products and services formerly contact east and jensen tools renamed in  usag italy – professional tools vidmar – industrial storage acquired in  virax france – plumbing tools acquired in  engineered fasteningedit emhart teknologies – fastening and assembly acquired in  later renamed stanley engineered fastening dodge – metalonplastic threaded inserts gripco – threaded fasteners helicoil – threaded inserts infastech – acquired in  by stanley engineered fastening avdel – blind fastening systems and related tools iform – coated threaded fasteners masterfix europe – blind riveting nprpop – riveting technology spiralock – threaded fasteners and inserts acquired in  by emhart stanley assembly technologies – assembly line power tools tucker – holeless fastening warren – custom fastening fabrication infrastructureedit hydraulic tools dubuis – cutting crimping and grounding tools horst sprenger gmbh germany – replacement consumables for scrap processing equipment labounty – nonimpact hydraulic attachments stanley hydraulic tools stanley oil  gas crcevans international – equipment used in the construction of pipelines for the oil and gas og industry securityedit convergent security solutions cssedit this focuses on electronic security systems and related services a reorganization of stanley security solutions stanley correctional systems and healthcare solutions resulted in a unified nonhardware business unit blick uk – security solution communication and time management systems integrator hsm niscayah ab acquired in  sonitrol générale de protection france stanley health care solutions – supply chain asset and patientresident protection systems aeroscout – realtime location systems rtls arial – wireless emergency call bedcheck – electronic fall monitoring innerspace  a provider of healthcare storage solutions and inventory management analysis innerspace also provides webbased supply management software that utilizes barcoding technology to increase charge capture reduce excess inventory and eliminate waste it was acquired in  hugs infant protection – infant abduction and mismatch prevention microtech enterprises – electronic fall monitoring mycall – wireless emergency call passport – adult patient elopement and flight prevention pedz – pediatric patient abduction and flight prevention roamalert – clinical and residential wander management scanmodul – healthcare industry storage spacetrax – inventory management tabs – electronic fall monitoring ump – electronic fall monitoring wanderguard – patientresident wander management intivid solutions – video electronics mechanical access solutions masedit these are physical access systems and associated hardware including automatic doors electronic keyless entry systems locking mechanisms and related keying systems best access systems – door hardware and locks acquired in  cj rush industries canada – revolving doors and entrance systems evs canada frisco bay industries ltd canada friscoatms canada safemasters sargent and greenleaf inc sielox security systems australia stanley access technologies – automatic doors stanley door closers precision hardware – panic and fire exit hardware stanley hardware divested businessesedit hardware and home improvement hhiedit these were sold to spectrum brands in  baldwin – acquired in  kwikset – acquired in  by black  decker national hardware – general hardware acquired in  price pfister – plumbing fixtures acquired in  by black  decker weiser lock – keyless entry and door hardware air compressors and pressure washersedit this was sold to mat holdings in  devilbiss air power – pneumatic tools b  d acquired in  now known as mat industries llc toolsedit husky – privatelabel hand tools for the home depot acquired in  later transferred to the home depot craftsman – privatelabel hand tools for sears up until the mids reacquired by stanley in  vector products – battery chargers power inverters and similar power products acquired in  sold to baccus global in  notesedit  company history stanley works retrieved january     a b swk  finance msn retrieved march     swk company  finance msn retrieved march     stanley and black  decker complete merger press release stanley black  decker march   retrieved march     patricks blood and gore leach leach  enormously detailed model history of planes manufactured by stanley  filearmynavy production award to stanley works presentation program january    new britain industrial museum  dscjpg wikimedia commons retrieved january      december   businesswire  a b c d e f stanley infomatnet nd archived from the original on july   retrieved august     wiktor kuc north bros manufacturing company  historical overview wkfinetoolscom retrieved august     stanley australia tools hand tool preservation association of australia retrieved february     about stanley vidmar stanley vidmar retrieved october     turner tools hand tool preservation association of australia retrieved february     a b c d e f overview stanley black  decker retrieved may     proto tools th anniversary timeline stanley proto retrieved august     stanley bostitch – our history stanley bostitch retrieved august     the stanley works annual report   langlois shawn november   stanley works buying black  decker in  billion deal marketwatch retrieved august    sentem